{"tid":576313,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"人類討厭返工卻湧着去被劈價，歸根究底是因為商家捅中了人性弱點","createTime":"2018-02-28T19:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T00:32:15.000Z","uid":172172,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dba5573862e25020d3c46e3ac1769ac264c893c5","tid":576313,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T19:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2018/02/28/176946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F176946&d=KAJfYNLaML4WSuj7codgJJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e420723f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2018/02/28/176946</a><br />\n人類討厭返工卻湧着去被劈價，歸根究底是因為商家捅中了人性弱點，乘著女權主義者為女性爭取工作機會的契機，將人類尊嚴與工作掛勾，由本來工作機會的開放，變做人人不去工作就不配有尊嚴的局面，然而人人可以去返工，和人人一定要返工，是兩碼子事。那邪惡的分別仿似，他們將你擁有玩跳樓機的資格，轉化成迫使你不玩跳樓機就會被指責為無膽匪類的處境。當所有人攬住份工來捍衛尊嚴時，被壓價其實是供求變化下必然會發生的事，而得益者只有商人，沒有之一。<br />\n<br />\n如果我們的思想夠進步，那就會知道，人生而有平等的尊嚴，是世界人權宣言裏很重要的訊息，那即是說，人類本來就應有尊嚴，<span style=\"color: red;\">何以現代人的尊嚴，卻還要依靠工作作為手段才能獲得？這絕對是商人鼓吹的荒謬，工作和尊嚴的連結，乃切切實實地延續了舊社會迂腐思維</span>，用另一種包裝手法，進一步合理化我們以經濟實力作為輕視、唾棄他人和伴侶的藉口，當人類產生信任危機，在這場供求遊戲中我們已經狠狠地輸了。試想，如果當初我們每個家庭，不論男女性別，都有人願意放棄工作專責家庭事務，打工仔除了不會有內外兼顧的負擔，市場競爭不那麼白熱化，工資亦不會被壓至今日的地步。問題的關鍵在於，我們都擔怕在這樣的意識形態下，沒有了工作便不能在社會抬頭，甚或被家人嫌棄，所以才中了商人的圈套。<br />\n<br />\n事態發展至此，尊嚴與工作掛勾的觀念已深植人心，連路人都會歧視那些無返工的人，即便人家既無傷害到任何人一條毛，又沒需要到陌生人施捨，但人們就是會看不過眼，甚至恥笑家庭主夫吃軟飯、譏諷家庭主婦是黃臉婆。而正因為這種歧視持續，許多本來不會爭飯食的人，也來加入戰團，在市場分一杯羹。<br />\n<br />\n其實要停止剝削，首先要消除歧視，因為只要人力資源的供應逐漸減少，老闆就再沒囂張的餘地。這個道理很簡單，如果到最後老闆需要十個人手，卻只有四個人來見工，你看他還會不會氣燄冲天地說：呢份工，你唔做，仲有大把人做？"},{"pid":"65f8eeb1c1b314ac2e7cacff7d7fc1f67291200c","tid":576313,"uid":45120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T19:47:09.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n所以綜緩先係贏家"},{"pid":"cf39fbdcd9cd25a59214dc3ab26a7b4827df71a3","tid":576313,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T19:49:54.000Z","msg":"教人拎綜援仲好啦<br />\n我都唔撚想返工呀 吸風飲露呀？"},{"pid":"e4b77c8ca4f6a5a60a15c3100077b8cf12fabb26","tid":576313,"uid":172172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf39fbdcd9cd25a59214dc3ab26a7b4827df71a3","tid":576313,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T19:49:54.000Z","msg":"教人拎綜援仲好啦<br />\n我都唔撚想返工呀 吸風飲露呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T20:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_socsecu/sub_socialsecurity/#CSSAal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_socsecu%2Fsub_socialsecurity%2F%23CSSAal&d=KAJfYNLaML4WSuj7codgJJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=56f24a67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_socsecu/sub_socialsecurity/#CSSAal</a>"},{"pid":"55d27e6ccb64ec32bffd7ba786b344c72bf323c4","tid":576313,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"@老貓"},{"pid":"140e2b2edd5bf49216af987aee2b8349e39141fc","tid":576313,"uid":50088,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:02:48.000Z","msg":"成篇文up 乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5beef735ab79474b407ca4f1a7661451e4e86459","tid":576313,"uid":168367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"140e2b2edd5bf49216af987aee2b8349e39141fc","tid":576313,"uid":50088,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:02:48.000Z","msg":"成篇文up 乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"咁都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似你有問題多d"},{"pid":"0a4eb1f92a4be52da29e7437422d228b392a87a0","tid":576313,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd996a07db0c86f8858c139cfd16aa63a2216675","tid":576313,"uid":38041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"140e2b2edd5bf49216af987aee2b8349e39141fc","tid":576313,"uid":50088,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:02:48.000Z","msg":"成篇文up 乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:24:03.000Z","msg":"有人打篇鴻文幫隱青發聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3218e64a859ca1401c01090a430964338938f80","tid":576313,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:28:11.000Z","msg":"共產主義階級鬥爭？<br />\n投資落員工身上，得不到回報不如唔請。請唔到人賺唔到錢不如唔做。"},{"pid":"b2cb757420606152c6c20ccb6a680ed155604750","tid":576313,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T00:32:15.000Z","msg":"香港既自然性失業率低到痴撚線"}]}